                <note rend="inline" type="source">890F.24/9–1145: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Saudi Arabia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Eddy</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-09-11T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >September 11, 1945—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>274. Lend-Lease assistance Saudi Arabia as programmed will be continued 1945
                    despite general discontinuance. Please inform SAG and British
                    representative.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
